409
00:37:47,150 --> 00:37:48,450
Firemná akcia.

410
00:37:48,450 --> 00:37:50,560
Akcia?!

411
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:54,260
Všetci ste mŕtvy! Pozvem Vás na drink.

