00:47:28,330 --> 00:47:29,330
Čo robíš?

454
00:47:29,330 --> 00:47:31,340
Kam ma udrel?

455
00:47:31,340 --> 00:47:33,500
Prečo spíš v mojej posteli?

456
00:47:35,540 --> 00:47:36,740
Tak to nie je ...

457
00:47:36,740 --> 00:47:39,750
Čo tým myslíš, že nie je? Si presne tu!

458
00:47:40,950 --> 00:47:43,650
Nenechala si otvorené okno?

459
00:47:43,650 --> 00:47:47,450
Prišiel som, lebo mi bola zima.

460
00:47:47,450 --> 00:47:49,860
Nenechala ...

461
00:47:53,960 --> 00:47:55,260
Čo sa stalo?

462
00:47:55,260 --> 00:47:58,360
Au! Au!

463
00:47:58,860 --> 00:48:03,050
To máš preto, lebo sa správaš k hocikomu ako idiot.

464
00:48:03,570 --> 00:48:07,200
Čo je to? Pekne ťa zmlátili.

465
00:48:07,370 --> 00:48:09,370
Koho zmlátili?

466
00:48:09,370 --> 00:48:11,680
Predstav si ako vypadá on.

467
00:48:11,680 --> 00:48:14,480
Skoro umrel.

468
00:48:14,480 --> 00:48:17,280
